GoldenEye:;

Shge saw a white animal stumbling around on the ground.  She flew 
down to catch it thinking it would make a good meal. AS shw swoped 
down, her internal scanners told her that the white creature was a 
bot.  She changed coarse and landed next to it.  She stayed in her 
golden eagle form and looked at the squirrel.
"Oh, hello there. Are you OK? You look like you could use some help. 
My name is GoldenEye.  What's your's?" She stayed still and tried not 
to frighten the little critter.
